    <item>
      <title>AustralianSuper 计划四年内将私募股权资产增加一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/australia-s-top-pension-plans-private-equity-spree-from-new-york</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国最大的养老基金AustralianSuper计划在未来四年内将其私募股权资产几乎增加一倍，因为借贷成本上升导致的平静期后交易量有所回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/australia-s-top-pension-plans-private-equity-spree-from-new-york</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 00:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市将因消费物价指数而被抛售，交易员对日元干预持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/asian-stocks-to-be-sold-on-cpi-traders-wary-of-yen-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和策略师表示，周三美国通胀数据快于预期后，亚洲股市可能面临压力，而货币交易员将关注日元可能干预的情况]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/asian-stocks-to-be-sold-on-cpi-traders-wary-of-yen-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 00:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债溃败，日本基准收益率创五个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/japan-10-year-yield-exceeds-0-8-as-us-cpi-boosts-treasury-yield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀飙升引发美国国债暴跌之后，日本10年期政府债券收益率攀升至11月以来的最高水平，而日元暴跌则加大了日本央行收紧政策的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/japan-10-year-yield-exceeds-0-8-as-us-cpi-boosts-treasury-yield</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 00:09:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于选举结果云改革前景，韩国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/korean-stocks-fall-as-ruling-party-suffers-major-election-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统尹锡烈的政党在议会选举中惨败后，韩国股市下跌，这可能对其保守的资本市场议程造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/korean-stocks-fall-as-ruling-party-suffers-major-election-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 00:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本外汇主管警告日元贬值后不排除任何选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/japan-s-top-currency-official-mulls-all-forex-options-as-needed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最高货币官员警告说，在日元兑美元汇率跌至1990年以来的最低水平后，当局将考虑外汇市场的所有选择，并准备好应对任何事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/japan-s-top-currency-official-mulls-all-forex-options-as-needed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:37:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商为伊朗袭击以色列做好准备，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员关注伊朗或其代理人对以色列的潜在袭击，这可能引发中东敌对行动的大幅升级，石油价格在三个交易日中首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国消费物价指数之后，全球债券抛售在亚洲蔓延：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高于预期的美国通胀数据强化了美联储并不急于降息的理由，亚洲债券大幅下跌，而美国国债则企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 22:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界外汇交易者对人民币的态度与美元一样多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/world-s-fx-traders-are-as-much-at-mercy-of-yuan-as-the-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些策略师表示，中国观察家呼吁北京放松对人民币的控制，但他们需要注意这可能引发连锁反应，从而动摇新兴市场和发达市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/world-s-fx-traders-are-as-much-at-mercy-of-yuan-as-the-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
